Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven has called for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What we have here is nothing more than\NRichard Braun's empty body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His soul will live on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us swear an oath on his soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue living on with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In Psalms 23 of the Bible…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hard to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lonely funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such an outstanding detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,yet not a single person from the police\Ncame to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His alcoholism caused problems\Nwhen he was in the force,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and he fell to his death\Nin a drunken stupor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the police say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after he died,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he apparently had plans\Nto meet with his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What… What have I done for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really just sit in my chair,\Nlisten to him talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, "You've made a full recovery"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that I've done for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can find him,\Nwe might be able to solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem strange, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This was no mere accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor was it a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard talked to his daughter\Nonly a few hours before his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with plans to meet the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you did what you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And Richard had made a wonderful recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop blaming yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to this, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since my husband was caught cheating,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't say a word to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Day after day, he washes his car\Nand tidies up the yard after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't even look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's better than him\Nnot coming home at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll go crazy\Ngoing through this every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you listening, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, I marched into the home\Nof that woman he slept with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And guess what happened, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminal intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There was none.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was simply an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, Richard Braun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,went up the rooftop of\NMunich University Building 12 on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,downed a bottle of whiskey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and fell to his death in a drunken stupor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you properly look into the bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We found Richard's fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you show me that bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard talked to his daughter\Nonly a few hours before his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with plans to meet the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this guy was definitely\Nin this bar that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember him coming here,\Nbut you don't remember if he came alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he ordered a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare for customers to come here\Nat that hour and not drink alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose he was with this young man\Nwhen he came?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We have tons of customers\Ncoming in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true that he bought whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written on the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Richard really the one who bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The bill just says\N"one bottle of Racke" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One bottle of Racke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the police notice\Nwhen they saw the label on the bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I only stick with whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet your room stinks of Racke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Racke? You must be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never drink that domestic crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be authentic Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rule of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard isn't the one\Nwho bought that whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to push me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have business with my buddy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Take this!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop dead, gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Act your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man like you should be\Nquietly taking care of his grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I trained with the border police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to push me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate\Na former police surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By a huge man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy I passed by\Nin the metro passageway handed me money
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and said to push you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought this for you, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's authentic Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted some, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That man's…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan's true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, Doctor,\NI gave my husband a piece of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him his infidelity\Nis like an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said he should get counseling\Nfrom you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, of course, Mrs. Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With the way he is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,my depression just keeps getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't really have depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about your husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,who silently spends every day\Nwashing his car and tidying the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange, no matter\Nhow you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take a look at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I should be free\Nthe day after tomorrow at 5:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That cheating man\Nis all brawn and no brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please fix him up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you've finished\Nyour examinations for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can go home now, Ms. Melles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Ms. Melles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you forgot to lock\Nthe back door again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot today too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up again…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the ad you put in the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's reminisce about how we cheated\Non that test. From Rudy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Will these words\Nreally get Dr. Tenma to contact you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he definitely will if he sees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a story\Nonly the two of us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, don't do anything rash\Nuntil he shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's one thing I want to look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the prostitute\Nwho called herself Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what Richard said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When Fahren, who committed suicide,\Nwent to go see that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there was another young man with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An attractive young man with blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll move with great care now\Nso we can expose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For the deceased Richard as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll call you again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Melles, you forgot to close\Nthe window this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot Langer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, her nickname now\Nshould be Sophie or something of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that fat old woman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're into, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Embarrassed at this age?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn at the second corner.\NIt's the second floor of the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she went somewhere nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, why does that old hag\Nget all the guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a super-rich guy used to visit her\Nuntil recently too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about you try me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a much better time\Nthan that old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably went somewhere\Nwith that new guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A new guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of acting her age,\Nshe's head over heels for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a huge man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy looks like\Nhe'd be big down there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay\Nif I clocked out for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, you work until five today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I have one last appointment\Nwith the cheating husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a date, right, Ms. Melles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you lock up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The prostitute named Sophie\Nwho called herself Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show her this photo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and have her testify that Johan was\Nthe young man with the deceased Fahren.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we would've been one step closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hesse. My wife made me an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try and visit\Nthat woman again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Mr. Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time receiving counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be nervous about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can relax\Nand talk about anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything said here\Nwill be strictly confidential,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so please relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't tell my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any worries?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Worries?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife found out\Nthat I was cheating on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really bored when I'm at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so I tidy up the yard and wash the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I spend every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make you feel a bit better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't speak to my wife at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that you can't,\Neven though you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the other woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you and the woman\Nyou cheated with no longer…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:19:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I had a dream where I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have that kind of dream often?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Often?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I haven't had one recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you cheated on your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it started when I met that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an attractive young man\Nwith blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many people I killed,\Nand even when I lost my country,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it was all like a dream to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But it changed after I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything looked real
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was no longer lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a bit thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you wait for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My secretary already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes tea so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame I can't serve it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see a lot\Nin your line of work, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you learn about\Npeople's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good comes from learning\Nabout dreams you don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the fact that I'm a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway… if you have any inclination\Nof starting over with your wife…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to speak with her again and…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you forgot\Nto lock the door, Ms. Melles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been guarding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're targeting you. Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
